advertisement-piratehumanoid-1 = Eyes sharp, boarders.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-2 = Keep formation and watch the corners.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-3 = Hold your fire until my mark.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-4 = Stay spread out and keep moving.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-5 = Check your mags and check your suit seals.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-6 = Patrol route clear so far.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-7 = Contact expected. Stay ready.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-8 = Boarding line, tighten up.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-9 = Cover the hatch and do not blink.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-10 = We take salvage, not chances.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-11 = Keep comms short and useful.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-12 = Eyes on targets, not loot.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-13 = Check-in complete, moving to next sector.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-14 = Keep pressure, do not overextend.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-15 = Sensors are noisy. Stay alert.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-16 = If it moves, identify first.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-17 = Keep your helmet lamps low.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-18 = Secure the corridor and lock it down.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-19 = Shift left. I want crossfire.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-20 = No heroics. We work as a crew.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-21 = Cover me while I check this room.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-22 = Breach team, report status.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-23 = Hold that angle.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-24 = I hear movement behind bulkhead.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-25 = Keep medics behind the front line.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-26 = Suppress and advance.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-27 = Keep your breathing steady.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-28 = Watch your step near the vents.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-29 = Fallback point is still green.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-30 = Two contacts on scanner sweep.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-31 = Do not break line of sight.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-32 = Fast hands, clean reloads.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-33 = Boarding party, status report.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-34 = We move on my signal.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-35 = Keep your distance and your discipline.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-36 = Confirm visual before you shoot.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-37 = Clear this deck and move up.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-38 = Keep the pressure on them.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-39 = We are not done yet.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-40 = Maintain comms silence unless needed.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-41 = Anchor this position.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-42 = Scanner ping at twelve o'clock.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-43 = Sector sweep complete.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-44 = Regroup and rearm.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-45 = Keep your heads down.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-46 = We hold until extraction.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-47 = Check corners. Check ceilings.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-48 = Stay cold and professional.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-49 = Contact!
advertisement-piratehumanoid-50 = In position! Over.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-51 = Sights are cold!
advertisement-piratehumanoid-52 = Radio check. Over.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-53 = Check in. What's your status? Over.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-54 = Spread out!
advertisement-piratehumanoid-55 = Keep your eyes open!
advertisement-piratehumanoid-56 = Lost contact with the lookout. Over.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-57 = Finishing my patrol and heading back. Over.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-58 = Command, what's the sitrep? Over.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-59 = Target on the move!
advertisement-piratehumanoid-60 = Command, we've lost contact with the search team!
advertisement-piratehumanoid-61 = Fan out!
advertisement-piratehumanoid-62 = Any word on those reinforcements? Over.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-63 = I could use some reinforcements, command!
advertisement-piratehumanoid-64 = Orders received and understood! Over.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-65 = Watch your step.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-66 = Confirmed. Over.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-67 = In here. Over.
advertisement-piratehumanoid-68 = Neutralize the target!
